event.title: was founded at the opening of the Cherokee Outlet on September 16, 1893

data.event: Ames was founded at the opening of the Cherokee Outlet on September 16, 1893.
On January 4, 1902, it was named for Henry S. Ames, a railroad official.

data.event: Oil was discovered within the Ames crater in 1991.
